[{"id":"7d83672319c2c1573820cedfd1156a34","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Catherine PARPET","to_list":[{"name":"Catherine PARPET","email":"CPARPET@DARROISVILLEY.COM"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re:","date":"2007-02-07T19:24:36.000Z","formatted_date":"Feb 7, 2007","formatted_time":"7:24 PM","body":"no it's ok\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Catherine PARPET <CPARPET@DARROISVILLEY.COM>\nTo: jeeproject@yahoo.com\nCc: Matthieu DE BOISSESON <MDEBOISSESON@DARROISVILLEY.COM>\nSent: Wednesday, February 7, 2007 11:55:26 AM\nSubject: \n\n\n\n\n \n \n\n\n<!--\n\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0cm;\nmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\nfont-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";\ncolor:#003366;}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{color:blue;\ntext-decoration:underline;}\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\n\t{color:purple;\ntext-decoration:underline;}\nspan.StyleCourrierlectronique17\n\t{font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\ncolor:windowtext;\nfont-weight:normal;\nfont-style:normal;\ntext-decoration:none none;}\n _filtered {\nmargin:70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt;}\ndiv.Section1\n\t{}\n-->\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDear Jeffrey,\n\n\n \n\n\nJuan Pablo Molyneux\u2019s lawyer, Ma\u00eetre Degroux, has indicated to me\nthat he submitted your ISF tax statements on last year at the request of Mrs. Experton, your lawyer in Belgium.\n\n\n \n\n\nHe\nwould like to know whether you see any inconvenience in his acting as Juan Pablo Molyneux\u2019s lawyer in the Guermantes\ntransaction. I do not see any real conflict of interest for him, but I would\nappreciate that you confirm the same.\n\n\n \n\n\nKind\nregards,\n\n\n \n\n\nMatthieu\nde BOISS\u00c9SON\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n____________________________________________________________________________________\n8:00? 8:25? 8:40? Find a flick in no time \nwith the Yahoo! Search movie showtime shortcut.\nhttp://tools.search.yahoo.com/shortcuts/#news","body_html":"<html><head><style type=\"text/css\"><!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --></style></head><body><div style=\"font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt\"><div style=\"font-family: times new roman,new york,times,serif; font-size: 12pt;\">no it's ok<br><br><div style=\"font-family: times new roman,new york,times,serif; font-size: 12pt;\">----- Original Message ----<br>From: Catherine PARPET &lt;CPARPET@DARROISVILLEY.COM&gt;<br>To: jeeproject@yahoo.com<br>Cc: Matthieu DE BOISSESON &lt;MDEBOISSESON@DARROISVILLEY.COM&gt;<br>Sent: Wednesday, February 7, 2007 11:55:26 AM<br>Subject: <br><br>\n\n\n \n \n\n<style>\n<!--\n\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0cm;\nmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\nfont-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";\ncolor:#003366;}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{color:blue;\ntext-decoration:underline;}\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\n\t{color:purple;\ntext-decoration:underline;}\nspan.StyleCourrierlectronique17\n\t{font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\ncolor:windowtext;\nfont-weight:normal;\nfont-style:normal;\ntext-decoration:none none;}\n _filtered {\nmargin:70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt 70.85pt;}\ndiv.Section1\n\t{}\n-->\n</style>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"Section1\">\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Dear </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Jeffrey</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">,</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Juan</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Pablo</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Molyneux</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">\u2019s lawyer, </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Ma\u00eetre</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Degroux</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">, has indicated to me\nthat he submitted your ISF tax statements on last year at the request of </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Mrs.</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Experton</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">, your lawyer in </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Belgium</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">.</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">He\nwould like to know whether you see any inconvenience in his acting as </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Juan</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Pablo</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Molyneux</span></font><font color=\"black\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">\u2019s lawyer in the Guermantes\ntransaction. I do not see any real conflict of interest for him, but I would\nappreciate that you confirm the same.</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Kind\nregards,</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#003366\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Matthieu\nde BOISS\u00c9SON</span></font></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"black\" face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: windowtext;\" lang=\"EN-GB\">&nbsp;</span></font></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div><br></div></div><br>\n\n<hr size=1>\nDon't get soaked.  Take a<a href=\"\nhttp://tools.search.yahoo.com/shortcuts/?fr=oni_on_mail&#news\"> quick peak at the forecast </a><br> with the<a href=\"\nhttp://tools.search.yahoo.com/shortcuts/?fr=oni_on_mail&#news\">Yahoo! Search weather shortcut.</a></body></html>","is_from_epstein":true,